      • getIconFromBase64

        public Bitmap getIconFromBase64(java.lang.String base64String,
                                android.support.v4.app.Fragment fragment)
        Decodes a base64 string to an icon for mapMarkers. Can handle normal image formats and also svgs. The icon will be resized to width: 70, height will be resized to maintain imageRatio.
        Parameters:
        base64String - Base64 string that will be resized. Must start with "data:image/"
        Returns:
        icon as BitMap, or null if there was a problem
